{"tid":1961311,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大聲公講嘢係襲警怕教唆市民話係法治，而手足係差館俾警察圍毆仲要擔心被屈襲警","createTime":"2020-04-06T16:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T16:49:16.000Z","uid":151057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38ede50180ea809afd42b74f535357812e7e530c","tid":1961311,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"「畀我揀多次，我都會話佢係懦夫。真係忍唔住，好興，又要無 number，又要鬧得咁大聲。」患有中度抑鬱的阿雄（化名），3 月 31 日晚在太子被捕後，因在紅磡警署向警員索要一條橡筋被喝罵「唔 X 得」，忿而指警員是「懦夫」。阿雄說，他其後被多名警員拳打腳踢。當日一同被捕的香港眾志成員李啟靖亦目擊事件...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B-pIX1QAjku/?igshid=nldynj9hhvl1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB-pIX1QAjku%2F%3Figshid%3Dnldynj9hhvl1&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lez2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=6a92a917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B-pIX1QAjku/?igshid=nldynj9hhvl1</a><br />\n <br />\n好好記住手足係俾邊個酷刑凌辱<br />\n邊個私刑恐嚇再屈襲警絲毫都唔洗負責 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}